commit.message: update dependency on Azure SDK for Python
add support for parallel blob upload
add zip_compression option for the blob file handler
allow hyphen included hostname as a part of table key
stay batch enabled on flush error
avoid invoking batch commit at exit when there's no uncommitted entity
avoid invoking batch commit on unused handler at exit
fix Base64 encoding error on Python 3
add Base64 encoding option for queue messages
rename Windows Azure to Microsoft Azure
